link: https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1HktVl9Zs93AZHDVIBsVWGHBBPpo_kDnUq4WHjoUarYQ/edit#slide=id.g45b6da3ca8_2_5


Fancy Todo Client

Buatlah client-side app untuk Fancy Todo kamu menggunakan HTML, CSS dan jQuery yang memungkinkan user untuk melakukan:

Register
Login
Create, Read, Update dan Delete Todo


reference: 
https://learn.jquery.com/
https://devdocs.io/jquery/
https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/localStorage
https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/sessionStorage
https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Cookies


link: https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1kb4tD5CucY_12ZJCiFnoO6D0_-c7w38ktcEtSuHelPA/edit#slide=id.p


Fancy Todo Social Login

Tambahkan fitur social login pada aplikasi Fancy Todo kamu.

reference:
https://aaronparecki.com/oauth-2-simplified/
https://developers.google.com/identity/sign-in/web/sign-in
https://developer.github.com/apps/building-oauth-apps/
https://developer.twitter.com/en/docs/basics/authentication/overview
https://developers.facebook.com/docs/facebook-login/
